content: As an AI, I don't have personal preferences or biases, but I can recommend tools that have been popular and effective for many users. That said, productivity and time management tools are highly personal and depend on individual needs and preferences. What works for one person might not work for another. It's important to experiment with different tools and techniques to find what works best for you. So keep trying new tools, set a system that works for you, and see how it can enhance your productivity and effectiveness in managing time for yourself.
